<div class="container mt-5 text-light">
    <h1 class="mb-4">Privacy Policy</h1>

    <p>Welcome to <strong>TheCutHub</strong>. Your privacy is important to us. This Privacy Policy outlines how we collect, use, and protect your personal data when you use our platform.</p>

    <h4>1. Information We Collect</h4>
    <ul>
        <li>Account information: your name, email address, and password (hashed).</li>
        <li>Booking details: selected service, barber, appointment date and time.</li>
        <li>Optional information: reviews, ratings, and comments you leave.</li>
    </ul>

    <h4>2. How We Use Your Data</h4>
    <ul>
        <li>To manage and confirm your appointments.</li>
        <li>To improve our services based on your feedback.</li>
        <li>To display reviews and ratings on barber profiles.</li>
        <li>To contact you in case of booking updates or service changes.</li>
    </ul>

    <h4>3. Data Security</h4>
    <p>We store your data securely using Microsoft SQL Server and apply standard encryption and authentication protocols. Passwords are hashed using industry standards. Access to sensitive information is restricted by roles (User, Admin, Barber).</p>

    <h4>4. Cookies</h4>
    <p>We use cookies to keep you logged in, improve navigation, and enhance the user experience.</p>

    <h4>5. Your Rights</h4>
    <ul>
        <li>You can view or edit your profile information at any time.</li>
        <li>You can delete your account upon request.</li>
        <li>You can contact us for data access or correction.</li>
    </ul>

    <h4>6. Contact</h4>
    <p>If you have any questions about this privacy policy, feel free to reach out to us at <a href="mailto:support@thecuthub.com" class="text-warning">support@thecuthub.com</a>.</p>

    <p class="mt-4 text-muted"><small>This policy was last updated on August 7, 2025.</small></p>
</div>
